description:
The Fourth Day Before Christmas: Episode Six is narrated by Joseph. He tells of the unwelcome news he receives about Mary being pregnant. He says that an angel of the Lord explained she was pregnant by the Holy Spirit and he should take her to be his wife. Joseph relates how he finds out that Mary is pregnant, his bewilderment, and the angel telling him how to obediently act. Eyewitness Bible Series is pleased to present the Christmas Series. This series is a collection of 10 new episodes designed to be watched on the three Sundays prior to Christmas week, plus the seven days of Christmas week, ending on Christmas Day. Scripture: Matthew 1:18-25; Luke 1:26-28
